channel.title: Domination - Tropical Original
channel.description:
Hello my fellow comrades, today i have a new track! Ive had this track for a month and did nothing with it till now, and it sounds amazing from my prospective! What do you guys think? I would love the comments to see what you all think.
If anyone would like to make special art for this song go ahead! Full credit goe's to whoever makes the picture. Ill put it in Soundcloud Description.
This song is Hard Bass / Techno. I'd recommend some headphones or a sub woofer to hear the epic bass! ;)
Soundcloud: [Domination - Tropical Original](https://soundcloud.com/tropical_madman/domination-tropical-original)
Ill be taking long brakes from song making to think of some new sounds and other stuff...
But in the mean time, You all have a wonderful day!
